{"tid":1068729,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【冰封3萬年保持原好】 【長毛象有望透過細胞組織復活】","createTime":"2019-03-19T12:16:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-19T12:16:49.000Z","uid":53379,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"3b56e9b75e3c1883763a6a3a0d29b934ffc50a8b","tid":1068729,"uid":53379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-19T12:16:49.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">【冰封3萬年保持原好】<br />\n【長毛象有望透過細胞組織復活】</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n將已經絕種的動物復活，是不少學者的心願。<br />\n<br />\n長毛象雖然早就已經絕種，但個別遺骸在嚴寒地區西伯利亞出土，保存得相當完好，能夠留下肌肉甚至完整細胞。<br />\n<br />\n一項由日俄學者合作的研究，利用埋藏了 2 萬 8 千年的長毛象遺骸，令細胞核再次展現有活動的跡象，向長毛象復活踏出重要一步。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/icablenews/videos/411495896091966/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Ficablenews%2Fvideos%2F411495896091966%2F&d=pHv7ulxaPAPTUdGhwq1YMR4w7aMtX%2B%2FJ%2BUdoe8qorTI%3D&h=267397ca\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/icablenews/videos/411495896091966/</a>"}]}